@inherits HowToFlashFirmwarePageBase

@page "/FlashFirmware"

<br />
<MudImage Src="./Projects/Images/esp32.svg" Width="600" Class="rounded-lg"> </MudImage>
<br />
<br />
<MudText>1. Install <MudLink OnClick="@(() => OpenBrowserTab("https://code.visualstudio.com/"))">Visual Studio Code (VS Code)</MudLink></MudText>
<br />
<MudText>2. Install <MudLink OnClick="@(() => OpenBrowserTab("https://platformio.org/"))">Platform IO</MudLink></MudText>
<br />
<MudText>2b. Optional Install WOKWI for VS Code if you want to simulate the ESP32 microcontroller (because you do not have a real one yet). <MudLink Href="https://docs.wokwi.com/vscode/getting-started">WOKWI</MudLink></MudText>
<br />
<MudText>3. Open the solution in Visual Studio Code with PlatformIO</MudText>
<br />
<MudImage Src="./Projects/Images/platformioopenproject.png" Width="600" Class="rounded-lg"> </MudImage>
<br />
<br />
<MudText>Navigate to the folder where platformio.ini is located and click button 'Open "Microcontroller"'.</MudText>
<br />
<MudImage Src="./Projects/Images/platformioopenproject2.png" Width="600" Class="rounded-lg"></MudImage>
<br />
<br />
<MudText>3. Open defines.cpp</MudText>
<br />
<MudImage Src="./Projects/Images/openmaincpp.png" Width="900" Class="rounded-lg"></MudImage>
<MudText>Comment in all #defines for the devices you want to connect to your microcontroller.</MudText>
<br />
<MudText>4. Open WifiSettings.hpp to Enter your WIFI settings</MudText>
<MudImage Src="./Projects/Images/usersettings.png" Width="900" Class="rounded-lg"></MudImage>
<br />
<MudText>5. Connect the microcontroller to USB or skip this step if you use WOKWI.</MudText>
<br />
<MudText>6. Compile and upload to microcontroller.</MudText>
<br />
<MudImage Src="./Projects/Images/upload.png" Width="600" Class="rounded-lg"> </MudImage>
<br />
<br />
<MudText>7. Optional: If you want to <b>simulate the microcontroller</b> press F1 into VS Code and choose Wokwi: Start Simulator</MudText>
<MudImage Src="./Projects/Images/startsimulator.png" Width="900" Class="rounded-lg"> </MudImage>
<MudText>Edit <MudLink OnClick="@(() => OpenBrowserTab("https://docs.wokwi.com/diagram-format/"))" >diagram.json</MudLink>. This file defines the components that will be used for the simulation, their properties, and the connections between the components.</MudText>
